---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'June 17, 2026';
const CONTACT = 'hello@spykeautomation.com';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Spyke Automation"
  description="The terms that govern your use of the Spyke Automation website and early-access program."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="legal" id="main">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p class="lead">
        These terms govern your use of <strong>spykeautomation.com</strong> and the Spyke Automation
        early-access program. By using the site or requesting access, you agree to them. If you do
        not agree, please don't use the site.
      </p>

      <h2>The website</h2>
      <p>
        This site describes Spyke Automation, an open-source version control system for industrial
        automation, which is currently in private beta. Information here is provided for general
        purposes and may change as the product develops.
      </p>

      <h2>Early access</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Requesting early access does not guarantee a spot. We invite participants in rounds and
          may decline or revoke access at our discretion.
        </li>
        <li>
          Beta software is provided <strong>as is</strong> and may be incomplete, change without
          notice, or be discontinued. Don't rely on it for safety-critical or production work.
        </li>
        <li>You are responsible for keeping any credentials we issue to you secure.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the site or program for any unlawful purpose.</li>
        <li>Attempt to disrupt, probe, or gain unauthorized access to our systems.</li>
        <li>Misrepresent your identity or submit information you are not authorized to share.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        The Spyke name, logo, and site content are owned by Spyke Automation. Our open-source
        software is licensed separately under the terms stated in its public repository, and those
        license terms govern your use of the code.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimers and liability</h2>
      <p>
        The site and early-access program are provided without warranties of any kind, to the
        fullest extent permitted by law. We are not liable for any indirect or consequential damages
        arising from your use of the site or the beta software.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Last updated"
        date above. Continued use of the site after changes means you accept the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Email <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT}`}>{CONTACT}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
